<header class="topbar"><div><div class="eyebrow">Cache traceability</div><h1>Generation request outcomes</h1><p class="subtitle">Every accepted speech request is classified by whether it reused existing work or started a new generation.</p></div><div class="top-actions"><a class="button" href="/admin/generation-requests">Refresh</a><a class="button" href="/admin/audio">Open audio library</a></div></header>
<div class="callout"><strong>Cache hit</strong> means the request reused an existing ready or in-flight cache entry and did not start another provider generation. <strong>Cache miss</strong> means this request claimed and started a new generation. Exact outcome tracking begins with this feature deployment; older cached files remain available in the audio library.</div>
<div class="filters" style="margin-bottom:14px"><a class="filter {{#if (eq outcome 'all')}}active{{/if}}" href="/admin/generation-requests">All</a><a class="filter {{#if (eq outcome 'hit')}}active{{/if}}" href="/admin/generation-requests?outcome=hit">Cache hits</a><a class="filter {{#if (eq outcome 'miss')}}active{{/if}}" href="/admin/generation-requests?outcome=miss">Cache misses</a></div>
<article class="card"><div class="table-wrap"><table><thead><tr><th>Requested UTC</th><th>Outcome</th><th>Installation</th><th>Audio / job</th><th>Current state</th><th>Voice / input</th><th>Playback</th></tr></thead><tbody>{{#each generationRequests}}<tr><td class="muted">{{date createdAt}}</td><td>{{#if cacheHit}}<span class="status outcome-hit">Cache hit</span>{{else}}<span class="status outcome-miss">Cache miss</span>{{/if}}</td><td class="mono" title="{{installationId}}">{{short installationId}}</td><td><div class="mono" title="Cache key: {{cacheKey}}">cache {{short cacheKey}}</div><div class="muted mono" title="Job ID: {{jobId}}">job {{short jobId}}</div></td><td>{{#if audioStatus}}<span class="status status-{{audioStatus}}">{{audioStatus}}</span>{{else}}<span class="status">deleted</span>{{/if}}{{#if errorCode}}<div class="danger-text">{{errorCode}}</div>{{/if}}</td><td>{{voiceId}} · {{number inputCharacters}} chars<div class="muted">{{bytes bytes}}</div></td><td>{{#if playbackUrl}}<a class="button" href="{{playbackUrl}}" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Play audio</a>{{else}}—{{/if}}</td></tr>{{else}}<tr><td colspan="7" class="empty">No tracked generation requests match this filter yet.</td></tr>{{/each}}</tbody></table></div><div class="pagination"><span>{{number total}} tracked requests · page {{page}} of {{totalPages}}</span><div class="pagination-links">{{#if hasPrevious}}<a class="button" href="{{previousUrl}}">Previous</a>{{/if}}{{#if hasNext}}<a class="button" href="{{nextUrl}}">Next</a>{{/if}}</div></div></article>
